OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate sunshine to end the day. Dry
OL,7,Fovernight, with increasing amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud cover once more, though southern
OL,9,Fand western areas holding on to some
OL,10,Fclearer skies.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMorning cloud clearing to
OL,13,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,14,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Temperatures a little lower
OL,16,Fin the north as winds turn northerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
