OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly dry into the weekend, with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunny spells. Some isolated
OL,8,Fshowers possible on Saturday.
OL,9,FTemperatures trending a little nearer
OL,10,Fto average, but still feeling warm.
